---
title: Ketjap Manis Glazed Beef Tacos with charred corn salad
description: Ketjap manis is a popular condiment in Southeast Asia (and beyond). In this dish, it's paired with sweet chilli sauce to create a sweet and tangy glaze which works wonderfully with the pan-seared beef.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R15_W10_IE_IEQB20965-2_Main__6high-e34c97fc.jpg
